Disease Name: Food or medicine allergies that affect the skin
Acquired or acute respiratory distress syndrome (ARDS)
Irritable bowel syndrome (IBS) or inflammatory bowel disease (IBD)

Missing a limb or part of a limb

Hit by car or other vehicle
Kicked by horse or other large animal
Immune-mediated hemolytic anemia (IMHA) or autoimmune hemolytic anemia (AIHA)
